listingPOs.name: Cradels
listingPOs.remarks:
Key Selling Points
Cradels is a freehold development built in 2015 by Melrose Land Pte Ltd, located in District 12 on Lorong Limau. It has a total of 125 residential units.
Whether its a night out on the town or a fabulous shopping spree at the malls, Cradels is the platform from which you can satisfy your every craving. With an enviable location near the city and surrounded by amenities, you are never far from the things you love.

Freehold Development in District 12.

Near City Fringe.

Proximity to hospitals and medical centres such as Thomson Medical Centre, Tan Tock Seng Hospital and Novena Medical Hub.

Easy access to Central Business District and other parts of Singapore via the Central Expressway (CTE) and Pan Island Expressway (PIE).

Open to sky deck Terrace on the 5th Storey houses an Infinity Lap Pool, Indoor/Outdoor Gym and a BBQ Area.
